
1  Enkerai ai, imbung'a irorei laainei, ninteng'el inkitanapat aainei tiatua iyie. 
2  Imbung'a inkitanapat aainei pee inchu, tagolie nkiteng'enat aainei anaa enerok enkong'u ino. 
3  Teeniki ninche ilkimojik linono, ingero ninche te mbao o ltau lino. 
4  Tiaaki eng'eno, “Ira iyie enkanashe ai” nimpot eng'eno nagut ajo olchore lai oleng; 
5  pee kitum atagolie te ina kitok naibor onyek, te ina aitang'oroni napuyiapui irorei.

Enkitok naibor onyek


6  Amu ore te lusie e nkaji ai, aturumishe aing'or boo te lusie ai, 
7  nadol tiatua ilmoda, namusu olbarnoti obo tiatua ilbarnot, oloti barnoti lemedamisho. 
8  Eim enkoitoi dapash e nkanasa embata enkaji e ina kitok, eibung enkoitoi alo enkaji enye 
9  pee mirimiru e nteipa, te nkata enkewarie o enkata enaimin. 
10  Naa ng'ura, nenang'are ninye enkitok, neishope anaa emulayoi, neeta enareuta. 
11  Neiro ninye meeta enkuretisho, metoni inkejek enyena tiang; 
12  etii te ina kata enkoitoi dapash e nkanasa netii tena kata enemirishoreki, ore te pooki lojata oo nkoitoi neton ninye aanyisho.


13  Neibung ninye ang'utut, ore inkonyek enyena nekurraki ninye: 
14  nejoki ninye, “Aidipa atalaa ilasarri, neaku ore ena olong atalaa ilmuma laainei. 
15  Metaa ore taata aaewuo atumore, aaing'orua iyie oleng, neaku aanoto. 
16  Aitobira endapash ai too lkarash oo puyiapui le katani naing'uaa Misiri. 
17  Aitorropilo endapash ai te manoo o esonkoyo o sinantei. 
18  Wou, maiputa ate enchipai ang omekenyu; matishipakinoto ate te nyorrata. 
19  Amu metii olpayian lai ang'; eshomo enelakua. 
20  Newa olbene loo ropiyiani nelo naa keshukunye kenya ang te mpolos o lapa.” 
21  Ore too rorei kumok le mpakasata, nearaki ninye; ore too rorei lenyena oo puyiapui neidimu ninye. 
22  Ore ina kata ake, nesuj ninye ninye, anaa olkiteng opuoi aayieng arashu enkolii najing atua orreshet. 
23  Ometaba anaa neng'or embae oltau lenye. Anaa emotonyi nakuetiki ajing atua orreshet; meyiolo duoo ajo keinosie enkishui enye.


24  Ore naa taata, nakera aainei, entoning'oki nanu niakuku ilooning'u lelo rorei le nkutuk ai. 
25  Mincho oltau lino eibelekenya asuj inkoitoi enyena, mipong'okino inkoitoi enyena; 
26  amu eitayio ninye ilmeneng'a kumok lemeikenayu. Ee, ore ilmeneng'a lenyena naa olorora kitok. 
27  Ore enkaji enye naa enkoitoi nalo enemeneng'a, nedoyio alo ilgilat le keeya.

